			<br/>
			to know
		</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-4 slogan">
			Unsolicited advice about life since 2015!
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-5 links">
			<%= link_to 'Contribute', '#' %>
			<%= link_to 'About', '#' %>
		</div>
	</header>
	<hr />

	<br class="clear" />

<div class="container">
<%= yield %>
</div>
<div class="footer">
<div class="container">
	
	<div class="col-xs-6">
		<%= link_to "Wait! I want to see more..." , "#", :class => 'next-quote' %>
	</div>
	
	<div class="col-xs-6 footer-blurb">Proudly hacked in Chico, CA<br/>by <a href="http://sandraharrasser.com" target="_blank">Sandra Harrasser</a>
